OL,7,FA satellite that aims to study clouds
OL,8,Fto make more accurate weather
OL,9,Fforecasts and reliable climate
OL,10,Fpredictions is gearing up for launch.
OL,12,FEarthCARE is due to blast off into
OL,13,Fspace on one of Elon Musk's SpaceX
OL,14,Frockets from the Vandenberg Space
OL,15,FForce Base in California.
OL,17,FIt is the brainchild of Professor
OL,18,FAnthony Illingworth from the
OL,19,FUniversity of Reading, who first
OL,20,Fconceived the idea more than 30 years
OL,21,Fago.
