OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F414A1716911346
OL,3,CSatellite that aims to study how
OL,4,Cclouds affect Earth's climate set for
OL,5,Claunch
OL,7,FThe project was adopted by the
OL,8,FEuropean Space Agency (ESA) in 2004,
OL,9,Fand later became a joint mission with
OL,10,Fthe Japanese space agency Jaxa.
OL,12,FIts mission is to collect as much
OL,13,Finformation as possible on clouds,
OL,14,Fincluding aerosols such as dust and
OL,15,Fsmoke that play a role in cloud
OL,16,Fformation.
OL,18,FThe satellite will also measure the
OL,19,Fradiation emitted from Earth's surface
OL,20,Fand atmosphere.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
