PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F414A1716911346
OL,3,CSatellite that aims to study how
OL,4,Cclouds affect Earth's climate set for
OL,5,Claunch
OL,7,FMany of its components, including the
OL,8,Fmain structure and two key
OL,9,Finstruments, were built in the UK.
OL,11,FData from EarthCARE ` which stands for
OL,12,FEarth Cloud Aerosol and Radiation
OL,13,FExplorer ` could help in mitigating
OL,14,Fthe threats posed by global warming,
OL,15,Fexperts say.
OL,17,FIt is scheduled for launch no earlier
OL,18,Fthan May 28 on a Falcon 9 rocket.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
