OL,7,FProf Illingworth, who is professor of
OL,8,Fatmospheric physics at the University
OL,9,Fof Reading, said it was a "humbling
OL,10,Fand thrilling experience to be part of
OL,11,Fsomething so significant".
OL,13,FHe said the EarthCARE data will help
OL,14,Fpolicymakers "make more informed
OL,15,Fdecisions about how to mitigate and
OL,16,Fadapt to the challenges posed by a
OL,17,Fwarming world".
