OL,3,CSatellite that aims to study how
OL,4,Cclouds affect Earth's climate set for
OL,5,Claunch
OL,7,FThe satellite weighs just over two
OL,8,Ftonnes (2,200kg) and measures a little
OL,9,Fover 17m in length.
OL,11,FOn board are four instruments that
OL,12,Fwill analyse clouds and their
OL,13,Fstructures in detail, take images, as
OL,14,Fwell as measure how much heat from the
OL,15,FSun is being trapped by clouds.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
