OL,7,FDr Ralph Cordey, head of Earth Science
OL,8,Fat Airbus Space Systems UK, said:
OL,9,F"EarthCARE is an important new
OL,10,FEuropean Space Agency mission to study
OL,11,Fhow clouds and dust particles affect
OL,12,Fthe way that heat is transported
OL,13,Fthrough the Earth's atmosphere.
OL,15,F"It takes a vital step in reducing
OL,16,Funcertainty about how the greenhouse
OL,17,Feffect works and will improve
OL,18,Fpredictions of how climate change will
OL,19,Fwarm the Earth.
