OL,3,CSatellite that aims to study how
OL,4,Cclouds affect Earth's climate set for
OL,5,Claunch
OL,7,F"With its payload of four instruments
OL,8,F` two developed in the UK ` and
OL,9,Fcarried on a satellite platform built
OL,10,Fby Airbus at Stevenage ` EarthCARE
OL,11,Fwill fill one of the remaining gaps in
OL,12,Four knowledge of our warming planet."
OL,14,FOther UK collaborators include The
OL,15,FNational Centre for Earth Observation
OL,16,F(NCEO), the universities of Oxford and
OL,17,FLeicester, Imperial College, and the
OL,18,FNational Centre for Atmospheric
OL,19,FScience.
